metadata.name: Queer Joy
metadata.description:
As a member of the LGBTQ2S+ community, I want to showcase queer joy and celebrate the strength and resilience of people living authentically.

I believe openness is an important step towards ending prejudice, but education is the key.

I will be donating a portion of the proceeds to my local non-profit community organization that works to demystify sexual orientation and gender identity in schools. (GRIS.ca)
